From: Aymeric Agon-Rambosson <aymeric.agon@yandex.com>
Date: Tue, 26 Dec 2023 18:20:01 +0100
Subject: Replace multiline Package-Requires with monoline

Forwarded: not applicable

dh-elpa is not capable yet of parsing multiline Package-Requires correctly. Work
is being done to add this feature, but we make do with this patch in the
meantime.
---
 lisp/git-commit.el    |  7 +------
 lisp/magit-section.el |  6 +-----
 lisp/magit.el         | 10 +---------
 3 files changed, 3 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

diff --git a/lisp/git-commit.el b/lisp/git-commit.el
index baecd6c..876da6d 100644
--- a/lisp/git-commit.el
+++ b/lisp/git-commit.el
@@ -12,12 +12,7 @@
 ;; Keywords: git tools vc
 
 ;; Package-Version: 4.0.0
-;; Package-Requires: (
-;;     (emacs "26.1")
-;;     (compat "30.0.0.0")
-;;     (seq "2.24")
-;;     (transient "0.7.4")
-;;     (with-editor "3.4.1"))
+;; Package-Requires: ((emacs "26.1") (compat "30.0.0.0") (seq "2.24") (transient "0.7.4") (with-editor "3.4.1"))
 
 ;; SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later
 
diff --git a/lisp/magit-section.el b/lisp/magit-section.el
index 52c44de..3f8291c 100644
--- a/lisp/magit-section.el
+++ b/lisp/magit-section.el
@@ -9,11 +9,7 @@
 ;; Keywords: tools
 
 ;; Package-Version: 4.0.0
-;; Package-Requires: (
-;;     (emacs "26.1")
